565
00:26:33,680 --> 00:26:35,839
Oh, yes.

566
00:26:36,359 --> 00:26:38,119
Some difficulties.

567
00:26:40,199 --> 00:26:41,280
You've worked a lot.

568
00:26:42,959 --> 00:26:43,800
Let's eat.

569
00:26:44,040 --> 00:26:45,040
-Come.
-Okay.

570
00:26:47,319 --> 00:26:48,959
Come, eat.

571
00:26:55,880 --> 00:26:56,959
What's wrong?

572
00:26:58,520 --> 00:26:59,760
No appetite?

573
00:27:00,280 --> 00:27:01,719
Are you having a fever?

574
00:27:03,400 --> 00:27:04,319
What's up?

575
00:27:07,880 --> 00:27:09,959
It's cold these days.

576
00:27:10,520 --> 00:27:13,599
Maybe, a little uncomfortable.

577
00:27:15,800 --> 00:27:17,520
You should sleep earlier today.

578
00:27:17,520 --> 00:27:19,680
Eat this. I'll buy some medicine for you.

579
00:27:19,680 --> 00:27:20,040
Okay?

580
00:27:20,040 --> 00:27:22,760
Uh, I'll go back to the university later.

581
00:27:25,680 --> 00:27:27,959
It's so late now.
