584
00:27:34,040 --> 00:27:36,680
I have to go back to solve the problems.

585
00:27:36,680 --> 00:27:38,400
But it's already ten o'clock.

586
00:27:40,160 --> 00:27:41,359
What's more, it's Friday.

587
00:27:41,359 --> 00:27:43,280
Didn't you just come back from there?

588
00:27:44,280 --> 00:27:47,280
