594
00:28:04,040 --> 00:28:06,800
You sleep on the couch tonight.

595
00:28:07,079 --> 00:28:09,359
What's more, when I work,

596
00:28:10,000 --> 00:28:10,959
you

597
00:28:11,239 --> 00:28:13,160
