598
00:28:13,719 --> 00:28:15,479
If you are beside me,

599
00:28:15,479 --> 00:28:16,959
I'll be distracted.

600
00:28:20,760 --> 00:28:21,959
Are you

601
00:28:22,719 --> 00:28:24,760
