602
00:28:25,959 --> 00:28:27,680
Can't I?

603
00:28:28,959 --> 00:28:29,880
Yes, you can.

604
00:28:30,160 --> 00:28:31,199
I like it.

605
00:28:33,719 --> 00:28:34,359
All right.

606
00:28:34,800 --> 00:28:36,079
You've cooked so much delicious food.

607
00:28:36,079 --> 00:28:37,160
Let's eat.

608
00:28:37,959 --> 00:28:39,359
-Let me serve rice to you.
-Um.

609
