00:29:22,079 --> 00:29:24,359
I told you not to disturb me.

611
00:29:27,160 --> 00:29:28,319
Xia Lin Xi.

612
00:29:28,479 --> 00:29:29,400
What time is it now?

613
00:29:31,680 --> 00:29:33,400
11:30.

614
00:29:33,400 --> 00:29:34,959
You should go to bed. Now.

615
00:29:34,959 --> 00:29:36,040
No.

616
00:29:36,040 --> 00:29:38,119
I'll have another project tomorrow.

617
00:29:38,119 --> 00:29:40,199
