to rely on at the weekend.

622
00:29:50,239 --> 00:29:51,920
-Come, go to sleep.
-No.

623
00:29:51,920 --> 00:29:54,680
-No.
-Stand up and go to bed.

624
00:29:55,479 --> 00:29:57,280
-Go to bed.
-I can't.

