00:29:57,280 --> 00:29:59,880
I'm always a top student.

626
00:29:59,880 --> 00:30:02,239
Being excellent is my tag.

627
00:30:02,599 --> 00:30:03,800
Although I'm in college now,

628
00:30:03,800 --> 00:30:05,760
I must finish my homework before I sleep.

629
00:30:09,359 --> 00:30:10,199
Xia Lin Xi.

630
00:30:10,800 --> 00:30:11,640
Yes?

631
00:30:12,599 --> 00:30:14,119
Are you hiding something from me?

632
00:30:16,400 --> 00:30:19,359
You think I'm holding out on you

633
00:30:19,359 --> 00:30:21,359
