634
00:30:22,520 --> 00:30:24,160
What you said just now

635
00:30:24,560 --> 00:30:26,839
is usually said only by Chen Yi Chuan.

636
00:30:27,800 --> 00:30:29,959
No.

637
00:30:30,119 --> 00:30:33,280
I don't have anything hidden from you.

638
00:30:33,280 --> 00:30:35,560
I'm just doing my homework.

639
00:30:36,599 --> 00:30:37,359
Alright.

640
00:30:38,520 --> 00:30:39,680
Continue your homework.

641
00:30:40,319 --> 00:30:41,560
I'll be here with you.

642
00:30:41,680 --> 00:30:43,119
I won't go to bed until you finish it.

643
00:30:47,239 --> 00:30:51,839
