644
00:30:51,839 --> 00:30:54,040
Go to bed as soon as you finish it.
Got it?

645
00:30:55,199 --> 00:30:56,160
No problem.

646
00:30:58,000 --> 00:30:59,160
-I'll go to bed.
-Okay.

647
00:31:00,319 --> 00:31:01,839
Go, go.

648
00:31:03,680 --> 00:31:06,760
-It's 11:30.
-Yes, it's 11:30.

649
00:31:09,400 --> 00:31:11,280
Sit down.

650
00:31:17,640 --> 00:31:19,160
-I'll sleep.
-Okay.

