00:32:14,560 --> 00:32:16,119
Why does she want to see me?

658
00:32:16,119 --> 00:32:17,359
I don't know.

659
00:32:17,359 --> 00:32:19,880
But she seems in a fury.

660
00:32:19,880 --> 00:32:21,040
Be careful.

661
00:32:21,479 --> 00:32:22,920
Yes, I will. Thank you.

662
00:32:22,920 --> 00:32:23,560
It's okay.

663
00:32:26,479 --> 00:32:27,760
When Miss Xia comes,

664
00:32:27,760 --> 00:32:29,119
