675
00:32:52,280 --> 00:32:54,479
What's more, he took the photos in class.

676
00:32:55,760 --> 00:32:56,880
Young lady.

677
00:32:57,560 --> 00:32:59,319
You'd better explain it clearly to me.

678
00:32:59,479 --> 00:33:02,359
You're here to teach

679
00:33:02,359 --> 00:33:04,239
or seduce students?

680
00:33:06,119 --> 00:33:08,239
I think it's better to ask him

681
00:33:08,239 --> 00:33:09,760
than make me explain it.

682
00:33:09,760 --> 00:33:10,920
Why did he take photos of me?

683
00:33:11,199 --> 00:33:12,640
It's his own phone.

684
00:33:12,640 --> 00:33:14,359
I can't possibly
make him take those photos.

685
00:33:14,560 --> 00:33:16,239
Sure, you didn't.

686
00:33:16,719 --> 00:33:18,040
But how could I know

687
00:33:18,040 --> 00:33:20,199
whether it wasn't you
who seduced him to do that?

688
00:33:20,680 --> 00:33:21,680
Mrs. Xu.

689
00:33:21,680 --> 00:33:22,839
Calm down, please.

690
00:33:22,839 --> 00:33:24,920
I think there must be
some misunderstanding.

691
00:33:25,119 --> 00:33:27,400
Several photos can't prove anything.

692
00:33:27,599 --> 00:33:29,479
Maybe he just did it for fun.

693
00:33:29,479 --> 00:33:30,760
It can't be so serious.

694
00:33:31,839 --> 00:33:33,280
Though Miss Xia is young,

695
00:33:33,280 --> 00:33:34,640
she's very experienced.

696
00:33:34,640 --> 00:33:36,199
She's also the top scorer of
the College Entrance Exam in Jiangming.

697
00:33:36,199 --> 00:33:37,359
So what?

698
00:33:37,880 --> 00:33:39,640
I just call it for what it is.

699
00:33:40,160 --> 00:33:41,239
A high score doesn't mean

700
00:33:41,239 --> 00:33:43,479
there isn't any problem with her personality.

701
00:33:45,479 --> 00:33:46,599
I'm talking to you.

702
00:33:46,599 --> 00:33:48,119
Where are you looking at?

703
00:33:49,160 --> 00:33:50,400
You don't

704
00:33:50,400 --> 00:33:51,959
respect others at all.

705
00:33:51,959 --> 00:33:53,520
The top scorer of the city?

706
00:33:53,520 --> 00:33:55,920
Look, students call you teacher.

707
00:33:55,920 --> 00:33:57,719
So you regard yourself as a real teacher?

708
00:33:57,719 --> 00:33:59,160
You don't deserve it.

709
00:33:59,400 --> 00:34:00,560
You put on airs with me.

710
00:34:00,560 --> 00:34:01,880
And you show me a long face.

711
00:34:01,880 --> 00:34:03,199
Whom do you want to threaten?

712
00:34:03,400 --> 00:34:04,400
Listen,

713
00:34:04,400 --> 00:34:06,400
my son took so many tutorial classes.

714
00:34:06,400 --> 00:34:08,360
I've never met a teacher like you.

715
00:34:10,399 --> 00:34:12,239
Mrs. Xu, please calm down.

716
00:34:12,800 --> 00:34:13,959
If there's any problem, we can solve it.

717
00:34:13,959 --> 00:34:15,399
Don't get angry at her.

718
00:34:15,600 --> 00:34:16,959
We can talk it out, right?

719
00:34:16,959 --> 00:34:19,080
Scolding her can't help you
solve the problem.

720
00:34:19,080 --> 00:34:20,080
Now, let's go outside.

721
00:34:20,080 --> 00:34:21,159
You can talk to me,
and I'll find a solution.

722
00:34:21,159 --> 00:34:22,000
Okay?

723
00:34:23,439 --> 00:34:25,239
This way, please. Let me help you.

724
00:34:26,360 --> 00:34:28,000
Mrs. Xu, what do you say

725
00:34:28,000 --> 00:34:29,080
if we transfer Xu Fan to another class?

726
00:34:29,080 --> 00:34:30,719
I'll make sure that
he studies in the best class.

727
00:34:30,719 --> 00:34:32,679
The teacher will be a very famous one.

728
00:34:33,199 --> 00:34:36,120
If so, can you not
file a complaint against her?

729
00:35:02,120 --> 00:35:03,879
Xia Lin Xi.

730
00:35:07,679 --> 00:35:09,000
You're greatly wronged.

731
00:35:09,000 --> 00:35:10,600
So you will quit the job?

732
00:35:14,600 --> 00:35:17,080
No, I need money.

733
00:35:22,280 --> 00:35:25,159
Lack of money isn't shameful.

734
00:35:29,600 --> 00:35:30,679
Miss Xia.

735
00:35:30,679 --> 00:35:31,919
Are you alright?

736
00:35:31,919 --> 00:35:32,959
I'm sorry to hear that.

737
00:35:33,280 --> 00:35:35,479
It's nothing. I was just misunderstood.

738
00:35:35,479 --> 00:35:36,840
Oh, I see.

739
00:35:36,840 --> 00:35:38,120
I'm fine, really.

740
00:35:38,120 --> 00:35:39,600
Don't think too much.

741
00:35:40,399 --> 00:35:41,560
-It's okay.
-Miss Xia.

