747
00:35:51,360 --> 00:35:53,360
-Take care, Miss Xia.
-Yes, I will.

748
00:35:53,679 --> 00:35:54,639
Don't worry about me.

749
00:35:54,639 --> 00:35:56,239
I'm really fine.

750
00:35:56,239 --> 00:35:57,040
Okay. Bye-bye.

751
00:35:57,040 --> 00:35:58,000
-Thank you.
-Bye-bye.

752
00:36:03,560 --> 00:36:04,639
What's up?

753
00:36:05,000 --> 00:36:06,320
That's how you take care of her?

754
00:36:10,719 --> 00:36:12,919
I thought that
you came for something else.

755
00:36:14,560 --> 00:36:16,360
I didn't expect that
it's for Lin Xi again.

756
00:36:18,520 --> 00:36:19,719
Jiang Zheng Han.

757
00:36:21,399 --> 00:36:22,879
You don't have the right

758
00:36:22,879 --> 00:36:23,879
