763
00:36:32,760 --> 00:36:33,639
or

764
00:36:34,159 --> 00:36:36,199
an honest winner.

765
00:36:37,600 --> 00:36:39,360
Because I think a real man

766
00:36:40,360 --> 00:36:42,639
